1818796363.text: "This increase in the AMP : ATP ratio correlated with concomitant increase in tamoxifen- induced AMPK phosphorylation of the downstream signaling target acetyl-CoA carboxylase (ACC) and dephosphorylation of the mTOR targets P70S6K, S6 and 4EBP1, in both MCF7 (XREF_FIG) and MDA-MB-231 cells (XREF_FIG)."
